---
export const prerender = true;
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Use — Littles and Me" lang="en">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-14">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl mb-8">Terms of Use</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-sm text-charcoal/80 space-y-6">
      <p>Last updated: May 14, 2026</p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-xl mt-8 mb-2">General</h2>
      <p>By using littlesandmeknits.com, Strikketorget, and Strikkestua you agree to these terms. The services are operated by Weggersen Design.</p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-xl mt-8 mb-2">Account</h2>
      <p>You must be at least 18 years old to create an account. You are responsible for keeping your login credentials secure and for all activity on your account.</p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-xl mt-8 mb-2">Marketplace</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li>Sellers are responsible for accurately describing their items</li>
        <li>Purchases are made directly between buyer and seller — Littles and Me facilitates the transaction</li>
        <li>A service fee is charged on each transaction</li>
        <li>Disputes are handled according to our dispute resolution process</li>
        <li>We reserve the right to remove listings that violate our guidelines</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-xl mt-8 mb-2">Content</h2>
      <p>You retain the rights to content you upload (photos, text, patterns). By uploading, you grant us the right to display the content on the platform.</p>
      <p>It is not permitted to upload content that infringes on others' rights, is illegal, or is offensive.</p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-xl mt-8 mb-2">Payment and fees</h2>
      <p>Payments are handled by Stripe. Payouts to sellers occur after confirmed delivery. Fees are clearly displayed before confirming a purchase or promotion.</p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-xl mt-8 mb-2">Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>The services are provided "as is". We do not guarantee availability at all times. We are not responsible for the quality of goods sold between users.</p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-xl mt-8 mb-2">Changes</h2>
      <p>We may update these terms. Significant changes will be communicated via email or on the website.</p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-xl mt-8 mb-2">Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:hei@littlesandmeknits.com" class="text-terracotta-500 hover:underline">hei@littlesandmeknits.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
